OL,3,CChristmas day drunk driver who injured
OL,4,Cfive after crashing car into wall
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA drunk driver who seriously injured
OL,8,Ffive people - including children - on
OL,9,FChristmas Day while "showing off"
OL,10,Fspeeding and using his phone behind
OL,11,Fthe wheel has been jailed.
OL,13,FKevin Thompson, 44, spent the day
OL,14,Fdrinking before getting into his
OL,15,FMercedes CLA with numerous passengers,
OL,16,Faged between 13 and 30 - with one sat
OL,17,Fon another's knee without a seat belt
OL,18,F- and driving around Blackpool.
