OL,3,CChristmas day drunk driver who injured
OL,4,Cfive after crashing car into wall
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FShortly before 10.30pm the car left
OL,8,Fthe road and crashed into a wall, with
OL,9,Fthe passengers - three boys aged 13,
OL,10,F15 and 17, a 17-year-old girl, and a
OL,11,Fwoman in her 30s - all suffering
OL,12,Fmultiple serious injuries.
OL,14,FThompson was also seriously hurt.
OL,16,FIt is thought Thompson reached speeds
OL,17,Fof around 70mph and was also
OL,18,Freportedly using his phone in the
OL,19,Fcentral console as witnesses shouted
OL,20,Fat him to stop and slow down just
OL,21,Fbefore the collision.
