OL,3,CChristmas day drunk driver who injured
OL,4,Cfive after crashing car into wall
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FWitnesses also described seeing
OL,8,FThompson drinking alcohol throughout
OL,9,Fthe day, with one saying he had
OL,10,Freceived a bottle of Rum as a present
OL,11,Fand was thought to have consumed a
OL,12,Fsignificant amount of it, Lancashire
OL,13,FPolice said.
OL,15,FThompson was detained at the scene and
OL,16,Fgave a roadside breath test reading of
OL,17,F91, over the legal limit of 35
OL,18,Fmicrograms of alcohol in 100
OL,19,Fmillilitres of breath.
