OL,3,CChristmas day drunk driver who injured
OL,4,Cfive after crashing car into wall
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe then refused to provide a roadside
OL,8,Fdrug wipe, the force said.
OL,10,FHe also reportedly told officers "I
OL,11,Fwas driving, its my fault, I'm bad,
OL,12,FI'm bad", Lancashire Police said,
OL,13,Fbefore answering "no comment" in his
OL,14,Finterview.
OL,16,FThompson was charged with five counts
OL,17,Fof Causing Serious Injury by Dangerous
OL,18,FDriving, Failing to Provide a Specimen
OL,19,Ffor Analysis and Failing to Co-Operate
OL,20,Fwith a Preliminary test.
