OL,3,CChristmas day drunk driver who injured
OL,4,Cfive after crashing car into wall
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FHe was sentenced, in Preston, to three
OL,8,Fyears and five months in prison. He
OL,9,Fhas also been disqualified from
OL,10,Fdriving for four years and six months.
OL,12,FSergeant Paul McCurrie, of Lancashire
OL,13,FPolice, said: "Thompson knew how much
OL,14,Fhe had to drink on Christmas Day. He
OL,15,Fknew he would be over the legal limit
OL,16,Fand unsafe to drive, but he did it
OL,17,Fanyway.
OL,19,F"As a consequence, the next few of his
OL,20,FChristmases will be spent behind bars."
